# (e.g., https://learning-goals-api-production.up.railway.app) to route all dashboard
# reads through the new backend. Leave unset to fall through to the old n8n webhook URL
# (NEXT_PUBLIC_N8N_WEBHOOK_URL). Production flip happens in Phase 9 cutover.
